We are going to make our cluster on AWS cloud as it has many benefits like security,flexibility and many more. 
Amazon web service is a platform that offers flexible, reliable, scalable, easy-to-use and cost-effective cloud computing solutions.
ADVANTAGES:
 -You can easily add or remove capacity.
 -Offers Centralized Billing and management.
 -You will not require to spend money on running and maintaining data centers.
